<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="{{ report.summary_ko | default('AI 트렌드 리포트') }}">
  <title>{{ report.title | default('AI 트렌드 리포트') }} — AI Trend Report</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-primary: #0f172a;
      --color-accent: #3b82f6;
      --color-official: #22c55e;
      --color-unverified: #f59e0b;
      --color-caution: #ef4444;
      --color-bg: #f8fafc;
      --color-card: #ffffff;
      --color-border: #e2e8f0;
      --font-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: var(--font-sans); background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-primary); line-height: 1.6; }
    header { background: var(--color-primary); color: white; padding: 24px 32px; }
    header h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
    header .meta { font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 4px; }
    .stats-bar { background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 16px 32px; display: flex; gap: 32px; }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat .value { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-accent); }
    .stat .label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #64748b; }
    main { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px; }
    .summary { background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .summary h2 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    footer { background: var(--color-primary); color: white; padding: 24px 32px; font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.8; text-align: center; margin-top: 48px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>🤖 AI 트렌드 리포트</h1>
    <div class="meta">{{ report.report_date | default('') }} | AI Trend Report Engine v0.1.0</div>
  </header>

  {% if report.stats is defined %}
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="value">{{ report.stats.total_sources | default(0) }}</div>
      <div class="label">수집</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="value">{{ report.stats.ai_relevant | default(0) }}</div>
      <div class="label">AI 관련</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="value">{{ report.stats.clusters | default(0) }}</div>
      <div class="label">주제 클러스터</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="value">{{ report.stats.verified | default(0) }}</div>
      <div class="label">검증 완료</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% block content %}{% endblock %}

  <footer>
    분석 통계: 수집 {{ report.stats.total_sources | default(0) }}건 | AI 관련 {{ report.stats.ai_relevant | default(0) }}건 |
    생성 시각: {{ report.created_at | default('') }} KST | 엔진: ai-trend-report-engine v0.1.0
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
